i&gt;Beneficios: 1) Para pieles: deshidratadas, propensas al acné y a manchas oscuras 2) Bueno para: Reparar, calmar e hidratar&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.es/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=tolees-21&#34;&gt;🛒 Visítala!!!&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&#xA;   Check the price of this item in other countries:&lt;p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=tolees0a-21&#34;&gt;🇬🇧 United Kingdom&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=tolees-20&#34;&gt;🇺🇸 USA&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.de/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=tolees0ca-21&#34;&gt;🇩🇪 Germany&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.es/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=tolees-21&#34;&gt;🇪🇸 Spain&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.fr/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=tolees0d-21&#34;&gt;🇫🇷 France&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🇮🇹 Italia&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.ae/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=rdkn01-21&#34;&gt;🇦🇪 Arab Emirates&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.ca/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=rdkn0d-20&#34;&gt;🇨🇦 Canada&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com.be/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=rdkn0c-21&#34;&gt;🇧🇪 Belgium&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.nl/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=lgtm05-21&#34;&gt;🇳🇱 Neederlands&lt;/a&gt; |      &#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.pl/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=rdkn073-21&#34;&gt;🇵🇱 Poland&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.se/dp/B00PBX3L7K/?tag=rdkn0a-21&#34;&gt;🇸🇪 Sweden&lt;/a &gt; |&#xA;   &lt;/p&gt;</description>
